@Mean Old Lady

In North America, millions, billions, trillions all go up by multiples of a thousand (the short numeric scale). 

In Europe and other parts of the world, they use the long numeric scale where things go up by the million. So our “billion” is a thousand millions to them, and their “billion” is a million millions. So a billion has 3 extra 0’s, and a trillion has 6 extra 0’s.

